  F_C \ -  \ 0.04  \cdot m_B \cdot g \ = \ m_B \cdot 0.102 \ \Rightarrow \ F_C \ \approx \ 2.74 + 0.71 \ \text{N} \ . 
  F_P \ - \ F_C \ - \ 0.04 \cdot m_A \cdot g \ = \ 8.7 \ - \ F_C - 4.16 \ = \ m_A \cdot 0.102 \ \approx \ 1.08 \ \text{N} 
 \Rightarrow \ \ F_C \ \approx \ 8.7 - 4.16 - 1.08 \ \text{N} . 
